---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Aopiya" description="From Guangzhou to the world. 25 years of craft, now shaping brands of our own.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 bg-ink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent-light mb-4">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-normal mb-8 leading-tight">Built in Guangzhou.<br>Worn Worldwide.</h1>
      <p class="text-white/65 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        For a quarter century, Aopiya has been the quiet force behind some of the world's most recognized bags. In 2017, we stepped into the light.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-bg">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-4">1999 — The Beginning</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal mb-6">A Factory is Born</h2>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In Huadu, Guangzhou — China's leather goods capital — Aopiya was founded with a simple mission: make bags that last. What began as a small workshop grew into a 50,000-square-meter facility with over 1,000 artisans.
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
            Word spread. International brands came. Soon, Aopiya was manufacturing for 60+ leading names across Europe, Asia, and the Americas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/craft.png" alt="Aopiya atelier" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <img src="/images/journal-2.png" alt="Italian tannery leather" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-4">2003 — The First Brand</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal mb-6">SUSEN: Art Leaves the Factory</h2>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Born in Dubai, SUSEN was our answer to a question: what happens when factory precision meets artistic freedom? The result was a brand that treats every bag as a canvas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
            Bold forms. Unexpected materials. A spirit that refuses to conform. SUSEN became the voice of young women who see fashion as self-expression.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-4">2010 — Classic Refined</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal mb-6">BAGCO: The Power of Softness</h2>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
            While SUSEN spoke to the avant-garde, BAGCO spoke to the woman who leads with grace. Classic silhouettes, refined palettes, and the enduring elegance that transcends seasons.
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
            In 2022, BAGCO underwent a complete brand upgrade — "The Power of Softness" — seeking a more intimate dialogue with modern consumers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/bagco-model.png" alt="BAGCO collection" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <img src="/images/chrisbella-model.png" alt="Chrisbella collection" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-4">2018 — Fashion with Conscience</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal mb-6">Chrisbella: Fashion Can Be Kind</h2>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Chrisbella arrived with a mission: to dress 300 million young women worldwide — beautifully, responsibly. Our zero-fur policy wasn't a marketing move. It was a statement of who we are.
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary font-light leading-relaxed">
            Today, Chrisbella operates hundreds of stores and authorized retailers across Europe, Asia, Africa, and North America.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-ink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 text-center">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-5xl font-normal text-accent-light mb-2">25+</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm tracking-wide">Years of Craft</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-5xl font-normal text-accent-light mb-2">1000+</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm tracking-wide">Artisans</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-5xl font-normal text-accent-light mb-2">100+</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm tracking-wide">Countries</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-5xl font-normal text-accent-light mb-2">60+</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm tracking-wide">Partner Brands</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-bg-warm">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-4">Trust & Standards</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal mb-8">Certified for Excellence</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-ink-secondary font-light">
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">ISO 9001</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">ISO 14001</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">ISO 45001</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">SGS</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">BSCI</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">GRS</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-border">Disney</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
